ActSoftwood Lumber Products Export Charge Act, 2006
PrecisPAYMENTS TO THE PROVINCES REGULATIONS which requires the Minister of National Revenue to distribute, among the provinces from which the softwood lumber products originate, the revenue derived from those charges, less any refunds and less the costs incurred by the federal government.
